[2] Uganda: WHO/AFRO situation report
Date: Wed 29 Sep 2022
Source: WHO AFRO tweet [edited]
https://twitter.com/HelenBranswell


UPDATE: #Ebola in #Uganda Situation Report (29 Sep 2022)

- 54 cases (35 confirmed, 19 probable)
- 2 recoveries
- 25 deaths (7 confirmed, 18 probable)
- 517 contacts identified
- 4 districts affected (Mubende, Kassanda, Kyegegwa, Kagadi)

